#MEM id=delivery-status source=/root/yvon/agent-department/COO/diana/skills/marketplace/delivery-status/SKILL.md
M|delivery-status|name: ring:delivery-status
M|delivery-status|description: |
M|delivery-status|Delivery status tracking and progress reporting. Analyzes repository against
M|delivery-status|delivery roadmap to calculate actual vs planned progress, identify delays,
M|delivery-status|and provide insights on velocity and risk trends.
M|delivery-status|- Delivery roadmap exists (from ring:pre-dev-delivery-planning)
M|delivery-status|- Need to check progress against plan
M|delivery-status|- Stakeholders requesting status update
M|delivery-status|- Regular checkpoint (weekly/sprint end)
M|delivery-status|- No delivery roadmap → create one first with ring:pre-dev-delivery-planning
M|delivery-status|- Planning phase only → execute tasks first
M|delivery-status|- No repository activity → nothing to analyze
M|delivery-status|**Runs after:** ring:pre-dev-delivery-planning, ring:dev-cycle
M|delivery-status|Every status report must be grounded in repository evidence, not estimates or verbal updates. Status answers WHAT is actually done vs what was planned.
M|delivery-status|| Phase | Activities |
M|delivery-status||-------|------------|
M|delivery-status|| **1. Input Gathering** | Load delivery-roadmap.md (required), tasks.md (required), subtasks.md (optional), current date |
M|delivery-status|| **2. Repository Scan** | Scan ALL branches, commits, PRs, releases; build activity timeline; identify task-related work |
M|delivery-status|| **3. Task Matching** | Pattern matching (branches, commits, PRs) + semantic analysis (code cnt vs scope) via specialized agents |
M|delivery-status|| **4. Completion Calculation** | Per task: analyze scope items found vs expected; calculate % done; determine status |
M|delivery-status|| **5. Variance Analysis** | Compare planned vs actual dates; identify delays/early completions; calculate critical path impact |
M|delivery-status|| **6. Insights Extraction** | Velocity trends, bug rate, rv time, code patterns, risk indicators |
M|delivery-status|| **7. Report Generation** | Save to `docs/pre-dev/{feature}/delivery-status-{date}.md`; include evidence links |
M|delivery-status|**Q1: Repository** — Which org/repo to analyze? (format: org/repo)
M|delivery-status|**Q2: Roadmap Source** — Options: File path (local), GitHub URL (raw), doc link, Paste cnt
M|delivery-status|**Q3: Tasks File** — Same options as Q2 (REQUIRED — not optional)
M|delivery-status|**Q4 (optional): Subtasks File** — Yes (with source options) or No (analyze at task level only)
M|delivery-status|**Q5: Analysis Date** — Today (auto-detect) or Custom date (accepts DD/MM/YYYY or YYYY-MM-DD)
M|delivery-status|```bash
M|delivery-status|git fetch --all && git branch -a
M|delivery-status|git log --all --pretty=format:"%H|%an|%ae|%ad|%s" --date=iso
M|delivery-status|git branch -a | grep -iE "T-[0-9]+|task|feature|fix"
M|delivery-status|gh pr list --state all --limit 100 --json number,title,state,mergedAt,headRefName
M|delivery-status|git log --all --name-only --format="%H|%ad|%s" --date=iso | grep -v "^$"
M|delivery-status|```
M|delivery-status|1. **Pattern matching:** Search branch names, PR titles, commit messages for T-XXX patterns
M|delivery-status|2. **Semantic analysis:** Dispatch specialized agt per task type to analyze actual code changes vs task scope
M|delivery-status|3. **Completion calculation:** Count scope items found (endpoints, tests, migrations) vs expected
M|delivery-status|| Signal | Weight |
M|delivery-status||--------|--------|
M|delivery-status|| PR merged to main | High (but validate scope completion) |
M|delivery-status|| Feature branch active | Medium |
M|delivery-status|| Commits with task reference | Medium |
M|delivery-status|| Code changes matching scope | High |
M|delivery-status|| Test files for task scope | High |
M|delivery-status|| Status | Criteria |
M|delivery-status||--------|----------|
M|delivery-status|| ✅ Complete | All scope items found; tests present; merged to main |
M|delivery-status|| 🔄 In Progress | Active branch; partial scope found; open PR |
M|delivery-status|| ⏸️ Not Started | No branch, no commits matching this task |
M|delivery-status|| ⚠️ At Risk | Started but behind schedule per critical path |
M|delivery-status|| ❌ Blocked | No progress for >3 days on critical path task |
M|delivery-status|```markdown
M|delivery-status|- Overall status: 🟢 On Track | 🟡 At Risk | 🔴 Behind
M|delivery-status|- Planned completion: {date}
M|delivery-status|- Revised forecast: {date} (if different)
M|delivery-status|| Task | Status | % Done | Planned End | Actual/Forecast | Variance | Evidence |
M|delivery-status||------|--------|--------|-------------|-----------------|----------|----------|
M|delivery-status|| T-001 | ✅ Complete | 100% | 2026-03-10 | 2026-03-09 | +1 day early | [PR #42] |
M|delivery-status|| T-002 | 🔄 In Progress | 65% | 2026-03-20 | 2026-03-22 | -2 days late | [branch] |
M|delivery-status|- Sprint 1: ✅ Done (2 complete, 1 partial)
M|delivery-status|- Sprint 2: 🔄 In Progress
M|delivery-status|- Velocity: X tasks/sprint (planned Y)
M|delivery-status|- Average PR rv time: X days
M|delivery-status|- Bug rate: X bugs per task
M|delivery-status|- [T-002 is on critical path, currently -2 days]
M|delivery-status|- [Action items with owners and dates]
M|delivery-status|```
M|delivery-status|Every completion claim must include at least one of:
M|delivery-status|- PR URL (merged)
M|delivery-status|- Commit hash with message
M|delivery-status|- File path showing relevant changes
M|delivery-status|- Test file path confirming coverage
M|delivery-status|Never report completion without evidence links.